trans-unit.source: Specifies the element type of the linked list.
Represents a node in a <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />.
This class cannot be inherited.
Each element of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> collection is a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>.

The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601> contains a value, a reference to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> that it belongs to, a reference to the next node, and a reference to the previous node.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601> 값에 대 한 참조는 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> 다음 노드에 대 한 참조 및 이전 노드에 대 한 참조에 속하는 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The value to contain in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" />.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> class, containing the specified value.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> that the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> belongs to.

A reference to the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> that the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> belongs to, or <see langword="null" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> is not linked.

trans-unit.source: Gets the next node in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />.
